<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.1.4">
<l>veṟpāl māri paḻutākki viṟalvā ḷarakkar talaivaṉṟaṉ</l>
<l>vaṟpār tiraḷtō ḷainnāṉkun tuṇitta valvi lirāmaṉiṭam</l>
<l>kaṟpār puricai ceykuṉṟaṅ kaviṉār kūṭam māḷikaikaḷ</l>
<l>poṟpār māṭa meḻilārum puḷḷam pūtaṅ kuṭitāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of Rāma with a strong bow who,</l>
<l rend="indent">having rendered the rain useless with a hill,</l>
<l>Sundered the five-[times]-four firm, thick arms</l>
<l rend="indent">of the chief of the demons with strong swords,</l>
<l>Is Puḷḷampūtankuṭi, full of beauty [from] walls [built] by craftsmen,</l>
<l>Platforms, lovely houses, palaces, and adornment-covered mansions.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
